metadata.name: Skull-A-Day Thank You #1
metadata.description:
This skull love icon was originally created by Noah Scalin to celebrate the first ever Skull Appreciation Day on June 4, 2010. 
https://skulladay.blogspot.com/2010/06/skull-appreciation-day.html

This is the first in a series of thank you tokens given exclusively to holders of Skull-A-Day collection NFTs.
